commits.content:
{
    "name": "db-ps",
    "version": "1.0.0",
    "description": "david bade -official",
    "main": "index.js",
    "type": "module",
    "scripts": {
        "test": "echo \"Error: no test specified\" && exit 1",
        "start": " node backend/server.js",
        "server": "nodemon backend/server.js",
        "client": "vite",
        "dev": "concurrently \"npm run server\" \"npm run client\""
    },
    "keywords": [],
    "author": "faridguzman91",
    "license": "ISC",
    "dependencies": {
        "axios": "^0.27.2",
        "bcrypt": "^5.0.1",
        "bcryptjs": "^2.4.3",
        "colors": "^1.4.0",
        "concurrently": "^7.3.0",
        "dotenv": "^16.0.1",
        "express": "^4.18.1",
        "jsonwebtoken": "^8.5.1",
        "mysql2": "^2.3.3",
        "nodemon": "^2.0.19"
    }
}
